'''天鶴座'''是[[南天_(天球)|南天]]的一個[[星座|星座]]。它的名稱來自[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]的[[鶴科|鶴]]，是一種鳥類。它是由[[彼得勒斯·普朗修斯|彼得勒斯·普朗修斯]]、{{link-en|Pieter Dirkszoon Keyser|Pieter Dirkszoon Keyser}}和{{link-en|Frederick de Houtman |Frederick de Houtman}}觀察和構思的12個星座之一。天鶴座最先出現在普朗修斯和[[約道庫斯·洪第烏斯|約道庫斯·洪第烏斯]]於1598年在阿姆斯特丹製作的35公分（14英寸）直徑的天球上，並被繪製在[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]於1603年出版的星圖[[測天圖|測天圖]]上。法國天文學家兼探險家[[尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊|拉卡伊]]在1756年依據[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]為座內的恆星命名，有些以前是鄰近星座，像是[[南魚座|南魚座]]的恆星也被納入。天鶴座與[[孔雀座|孔雀座]]、[[杜鵑座|杜鵑座]]、[[鳳凰座|鳳凰座]]統稱為「南方鳥類」。

星座內最亮的恆星是[[天鶴座α|鶴一]]（天鶴座α），[[視星等|視星等]]1.7等，是顆藍白色的恆星。[[天鶴座β|鶴二]] （天鶴座β）是顆[[紅巨星|紅巨星]][[變星|變星]]，最大亮度2.0等，最暗2.3等。有六顆恆星被發現有[[系外行星|系外行星]]環繞：紅矮星[[葛利斯832|葛利斯832]]是最靠近地球的行星系統之一。其他還有 —[[WASP-95|WASP-95]]— 有一顆每2天繞行一周的行星。在天鶴座發現的[[深空天體|深空天體]]包括被稱為「備胎星雲」的[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]][[IC_5148|IC 5148]]，和被稱為「天鶴四重奏」，由4個星系聚集成的集團。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Grus_and_Piscis_Austrinus_from_Atlas_Coelestis.jpg|thumbnail]]，在{{link-en|約翰·多貝瑪亞|Johann Doppelmayr}}（大約西元1742年）的''Atlas Coelestis''曾經被描述為單一的星座。]]
[[File:Johann_Bayer_-_Uraniometria_-_Southern_Birds.jpg|thumb]]的''[[測天圖|測天圖]]''中所描述的「南方鳥類」。]]

組成天鶴座的恆星最初被認為是鄰近星座[[南魚座|南魚座]]的一部分，而[[敗臼一|敗臼一]]被視為魚尾的一部分<ref name=tiriongrus>{{cite web | url=http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/grus.htm | title=Grus | work=Star Tales | author=[[Ian_Ridpath|Ridpath, Ian]] | publisher=self-published | accessdate=8 February 2014 | archive-date=2020-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530105859/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/grus.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這些恆星最初是被荷蘭天文學家[[彼得勒斯·普朗修斯|彼得勒斯·普朗修斯]]根據荷蘭探險家{{link-en|Pieter Dirkszoon Keyser|Pieter Dirkszoon Keyser}}和{{link-en|Frederick de Houtman|Frederick de Houtman}}在前往[[東印度群島|東印度群島]]，被稱為{{link-en|第一次荷蘭遠征印尼| First Dutch Expedition to Indonesia}}的貿易考察航程，對南方天空的觀測創造了12個星座，並定義天鶴座成為一個單獨的星座。天鶴座首次出現是在普朗修斯和[[約道庫斯·洪第烏斯|約道庫斯·洪第烏斯]]於1598年在[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]製作的直徑35公分天球上。首此出現在星座圖譜上則是[[約翰·拜耳|約翰·拜耳]]於1603年出版的[[測天圖|測天圖]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/bayer%20southern.htm | title=Bayer's Southern Star Chart | work=Star Tales | author=Ridpath, Ian | publisher=self-published | accessdate=18 August 2013 | archive-date=2020-08-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821033042/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/bayer%20southern.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。De Houtman在同一年以荷蘭文出版的星圖包括這些南方的星座，在隨附的星表中將這個星座稱為「蒼鷺」（''Den Reygher''）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/startales1c.htm#houtman | title=Frederick de Houtman's catalogue | work=Star Tales | author=Ridpath, Ian | publisher=self-published | accessdate=15 August 2013 | archive-date=2020-08-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821031027/http://www.ianridpath.com/startales/startales1c.htm#houtman | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是拜耳依據普朗修斯和洪第烏斯使用鶴來命名這個星座<ref name=tiriongrus/>。

一個可以替代這個星座的名稱是''[[火烈鳥|火烈鳥]]''（''Phoenicopterus''，拉丁語：{{lang|la|flamingo}}），在17世紀早期，1605年被[[萊頓大學|萊頓大學]]的Paul Merula和荷蘭的天球 製作者Pieter van den Keere 在1625年短暫的使用著。天文學家Ian Ridpath曾經報告這個名稱可能源自曾經和這兩人合作過的普朗修斯<ref name=tiriongrus/>。天鶴座和鄰近的[[鳳凰座|鳳凰座]]、[[杜鵑座|杜鵑座]]和[[孔雀座|孔雀座]]統稱為「南方鳥類」 <ref name="binocs">{{cite book|last=Moore|first=Patrick|author-link=Patrick Moore|title=Exploring the Night Sky with Binoculars|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge, United Kingdom|date=2000|page=48|isbn=978-0-521-79390-2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Jvbtl2Vyxm4C&pg=PA48|access-date=2017-11-17|archive-date=2019-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730101729/https://books.google.com/books?id=Jvbtl2Vyxm4C&pg=PA48|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

與鶴相對應的恆星一般都在從中國看不見的南方天空。在[[中國天文學|中國天文學]]，敗臼一（天鶴座γ）、敗臼二（天鶴座λ）和南魚座的一些恆星，應該已經包括在浴缸型的星官[[敗臼_(星官)|敗臼]]中<ref name=tiriongrus/>。在澳大利亞中部，生活在{{link-en|Hermannsburg|Hermannsburg, Northern Territory}}的{{link-en|Arrernte |Upper Arrernte language}}和{{link-en|Luritja|Luritja dialect}}人，將天空劃分為兩邊：在[[銀河|銀河]]以東代表Arrernte集團，以西代表Luritja集團。[[天鶴座α|天鶴一]]和[[天鶴座β|天鶴二]]，連同[[北落師門|北落師門]]、[[孔雀十一|孔雀十一]]（孔雀座α）和[[蒼蠅座|蒼蠅座]]的恆星，都屬於Arrernte <ref name="noctuary">{{cite book|last=Johnson|first=Diane|title=Night Skies of Aboriginal Australia: a Noctuary|url=https://archive.org/details/nightskiesofabor0000john|publisher=University of Sydney|location=Darlington, New South Wales|date=1998|pages=[https://archive.org/details/nightskiesofabor0000john/page/70 70]–72|isbn=1-86451-356-X}}</ref>。

== 特色 ==

=== 恆星 ===
{{see also|天鶴座恆星列表}}
[[Image:Constellation_Grus.jpg|thumb]]

Keyser和de Houtman分配了12顆恆星給這個星座<ref name=knobel>{{cite journal | title = On Frederick de Houtman's Catalogue of Southern Stars, and the Origin of the Southern Constellations | author = [[Edward_Knobel|Knobel, Edward B.]] | journal = [[Monthly_Notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 77 | issue = 5 | pages = 414–32 [430] | bibcode = 1917MNRAS..77..414K | url = http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1917MNRAS..77..414K/0000414.000.html | date = 1917 | doi = 10.1093/mnras/77.5.414 | access-date = 2017-11-17 | archive-date = 2019-07-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190728143253/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1917MNRAS..77..414K/0000414.000.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。拜耳在他的星圖上繪製了天鶴座，但沒有指定恆星的[[拜耳命名法|拜耳名稱]]。法國天文學家兼探險家[[尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊|拉卡伊]]在1756年命名了從α到φ，但是漏掉了幾顆。在1879年，美國天文學家[[班傑明·阿普索普·古爾德|班傑明·阿普索普·古爾德]]捕列了κ、ν、ο和χ，這些都是拉卡伊已經編進目錄，但是沒有拜耳名稱的恆星。拉卡伊考慮到這些恆星都太暗，但古爾德並不認同，反而認為拉卡伊的σ太暗而將它刪除。此外，天鶴座χ原本位於顯微鏡座<ref name="wagman">{{cite book  | last = Wagman  | first = Morton  | date = 2003  | title = Lost Stars: Lost, Missing and Troublesome Stars from the Catalogues of Johannes Bayer, Nicholas Louis de Lacaille, John Flamsteed, and Sundry Others  | publisher = The McDonald & Woodward Publishing Company  | location = Blacksburg, Virginia  | isbn = 978-0-939923-78-6 |pages=360–62}}</ref><!-- cites previous three sentences -->。

天鶴座有幾顆明亮的恆星，標誌著左翼的鶴一（天鶴座α）<ref name=knobel/>，是一顆光譜型為B6V的藍白色星，[[視星等|視星等]]1.7等，距離地球大約101[[光年|光年]]<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Alpha+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = Alpha Gruis – High Proper-motion Star |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 1 December 2013 |archive-date = 2018-07-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180731213144/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Alpha+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url = no }}</ref>。它的固有名稱是Alnair，意思是「明亮的一顆」並且提到它是天鶴座最亮的一顆恆星。鶴一的[[光度|光度]]是[[太陽|太陽]]的380倍，直徑超過太陽的3倍<ref name="kaleralpha">{{cite web|url=http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alnair.html|title=Al Nair|last=Kaler|first=James B|author-link=James B. Kaler|work=Stars|publisher=University of Illinois|accessdate=1 December 2013|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104221217/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alnair.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。距離鶴一5度<ref name="motz"/>，代表心臟的是鶴二（天鶴座β）<ref name=knobel/>，這是顆光譜型為M5III的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Beta+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = Beta Gruis – Pulsating Variable Star |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 1 December 2013 |archive-date = 2018-07-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180731183215/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Beta+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url = no }}</ref>。它的直徑達到0.8[[天文單位|天文單位]]（如果放在太陽系將會延伸近金星軌道），距離地球大約170光年。它也是一顆[[變星|變星]]，變光範圍在2.0至2.3等之間<ref name="kalerbeta">{{cite web|url=http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/betagru.html|title=Beta Gruis|last=Kaler|first=James B|author-link=James B. Kaler|work=Stars|publisher=University of Illinois|accessdate=1 December 2013|archive-date=2017-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171104072619/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/betagru.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。從[[飛馬座|飛馬座]]的四邊形劃一條通過北落師門的假想線，繼續延伸就可以找到鶴一和鶴二<ref name="moore01"/>

位於星座的西北角，被標示為鶴眼的是敗臼一（天鶴座γ）<ref name="motz">{{cite book|last=Motz|first=Lloyd|author2=Nathanson, Carol|title=The Constellations: An Enthusiast's Guide to the Night Sky|publisher=Aurum Press|location=London, United Kingdom|date=1991|page=370|isbn=978-1-85410-088-7}}</ref>，是光譜型B8III的藍白色[[次巨星|次巨星]]，距離地球大約211光年<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=GAmma+Gruis&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = Gamma Gruis |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 4 December 2013 |archive-date = 2017-12-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171206202450/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=GAmma+Gruis&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url = no }}</ref>。它的傳統名字是Al Dhanab，已經完成核心的氫融合成氦的反應，並開始膨脹而使表面溫度下降，將會使它成為一顆紅巨星<ref name="kalergamma">{{cite web|url=http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/aldhanab.html|title=Al Dhanab|last=Kaler|first=James B|author-link=James B. Kaler|work=Stars|publisher=University of Illinois|accessdate=4 December 2013|archive-date=2017-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205230205/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/aldhanab.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在天鶴座有幾對肉眼可以看見的[[雙星|雙星]]。鶴一、鶴二與相距45角秒的雙星[[鶴增二|鶴增二]]（天鶴座δ<sup>1</sup>）和{{link-en|鶴十一|Delta2 Gruis}}（天鶴座δ<sup>2</sup>）形成一個三角形<ref name="motz"/>。鶴增二是一顆光譜類型G7III、視星等4.0的[[黃巨星|黃巨星]]，距離地球約309光年<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=del1+gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = HR 8556 – Star in double system |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 19 January 2014 |archive-date = 2017-12-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171206210953/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=del1+gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並且可能有視星等12等[[K型主序星|橙矮星]]伴星<ref name="kalerdelta">{{cite web|url=http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/deltagru.html|title=Delta Gruis|last=Kaler|first=James B|author-link=James B. Kaler|work=Stars|publisher=University of Illinois|accessdate=26 January 2014|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206074556/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/deltagru.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鶴十一是光譜類型M4.5III半規則變星的紅巨星，變光範圍介於3.99和4.2之間<ref name=AAVSOdel2>{{cite web|url=http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=14810|title=Delta 2 Gruis|author=Watson, Christopher|date=25 August 2009|work=AAVSO Website|publisher=American Association of Variable Star Observers|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826030222/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=14810|dead-url=no}}</ref>，距離地球約325光年。它的質量大約是太陽的3倍，直徑則是太陽的135倍<ref name="kalerdelta"/>。天鶴μ是鶴十二（天鶴座μ<sup>1</sup>）和鶴增一（天鶴座μ<sup>2</sup>）組成的光學雙星，兩顆星的光譜類型都是G8III，質量大約是太陽的2.5倍，表面溫度大約4,900K<ref name="kalermu">{{cite web|url=http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/mugru.html|title=Mu Gruis|last=Kaler|first=James B|author-link=James B. Kaler|work=Stars|publisher=University of Illinois|accessdate=26 January 2014|archive-date=2017-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205214336/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/mugru.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鶴十二比較亮，視星等4.8，距離地球大約275光年<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbak.cfa.harvard.edu/simbad/sim-basic?Ident=HD+211088&submit=SIMBAD+search |title = HR 8486 |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 19 January 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> while Mu<sup>2</sup>。較暗的鶴增一視星等5.11，距離地球約265光年<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbak.cfa.harvard.edu/simbad/sim-id?Ident=mu2+gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = HR 8488 |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 19 January 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。天鶴座π是一對雙星，也是一對變星。天鶴座π<sup>1</sup>是[[半規則變星|半規則變星]]的[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]，光譜類型為S5，變光範圍在5.31－7.01等，週期為191天<ref name=AAVSOpi1>{{cite web |url=http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=14811 |title=Pi 1 Gruis |author=Otero, Sebastian Alberto |date=20 June 2011 |work=AAVSO Website |publisher=American Association of Variable Star Observers |accessdate=19 January 2014 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206214146/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=14811 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，距離地球大約532光年<ref>{{cite web|url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Pi1+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id|title = Pi1 Gruis – S Star|work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database|publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg|accessdate = 19 January 2014|archive-date = 2017-12-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171206202854/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Pi1+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id|dead-url = no}}</ref>。它是從地球可以看見的S型恆星中最亮的，它有一顆類似太陽的半星，視星等10.9，是一顆光譜類型G0V的[[G型主序星|黃主序星]]。這一對可能是[[聯星|聯星]]<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Sacuto, S. |author2=Jorissen, A. |author3=Cruzalèbes, P. |author4=Chesneau, O. |author5=Ohnaka, K. |author6=Quirrenbach, A. |author7=Lopez, B. |date=2008|title=The close circumstellar environment of the semi-regular S-type star π 1 Gruis|journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics|volume=482|issue=2|pages=561–74| bibcode=2008A&A...482..561S|arxiv = 0803.3077 |doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20078306 }}</ref>。天鶴座π<sup>2</sup>是一顆光譜類型為F3III-IV的[[巨星|巨星]]，距離地球130光年<ref>{{cite web|url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Pi2+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id|title = LTT 8994 – High proper-motion Star|work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database|publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg|accessdate = 19 January 2014|archive-date = 2017-12-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171206215126/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Pi2+Gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id|dead-url = no}}</ref>，通常比它的伴星明亮，視星等5.6等{{sfn|Ridpath|Tirion|2001|pp=152–53}}。標誌右翼的是鶴八（天鶴座θ）<ref name=knobel/>，是另一對雙星，在鶴增二和鶴十一東方約5度<ref name="motz"/>。

[[天鶴座RZ|天鶴座RZ]]是一對視星等12.3等，偶爾會變暗至13.4等的聯星，它的成員——白矮星和主序星——被認為以大約8.5到10小時的週期在軌道上互繞。這個系統被歸類為[[激變變星|激變變星]]的大熊座UX型變星，其中的物質從施主星（主序星）流向白矮星，形成一個[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]，維持著在兩顆恆星之外閃耀的亮度。對這個系統的了解不多<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Bisol, Alexandra C. |author2=Godon, Patrick |author3=Sion, Edward M. |date=2012|title=Far Ultraviolet Spectroscopy of Three Long Period Nova-Like Variables|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|volume=124|issue=912|pages=158–63|bibcode=2012PASP..124..158B|arxiv = 1112.3711 |doi = 10.1086/664464 }}</ref>，然而施主星被計算是光譜型F5V的主序星<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Stickland, D.J.|author2=Kelly, B.D.|author3=Cooke, J.A.|author4=Coulson, I.|author5=Engelbrecht, C.|author6=Kilkenny, D.|date=1984|title=RZ Gru – A UX UMa 'disc star'|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|volume=206|pages=819–31|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1984MNRAS.206..819S/0000819.000.html|bibcode=1984MNRAS.206..819S|doi=10.1093/mnras/206.4.819|access-date=2017-12-08|archive-date=2019-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728131551/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1984MNRAS.206..819S/0000819.000.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 這些恆星的光譜與新星相似，在爆發後後會恢復平靜，但未曾觀察到其爆發過。 [[美國變星觀測者協會|美國變星觀測者協會]]建議觀測它們未來的事件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aavso.org/vsots_uxuma|title=UX Ursae Majoris|last=Malatesta|first=Kerri|date=17 July 2010|work=Variable Star of the Season|accessdate=26 January 2014|archive-date=2017-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208122432/http://www.aavso.org/vsots_uxuma|dead-url=no}}</ref><!-- cites previous two sentences --> {{link-en|天鶴座CF|CE Gruis}}（也稱為天鶴V-1）是由白矮星和施主星組成的一個暗弱的系統（星等18-21等）；這兩顆星如此的接近，因此已經[[潮汐鎖定|潮汐鎖定]]。已知是[[高偏振星|高偏振星]]，來自施主星的物質不會在白矮星周圍形成吸積盤，而是直接流到它上面<ref name="ramsay02">{{cite journal|author1=Ramsay, Gavin|author2=Cropper, Mark|date=2002|title=First X-ray Observations of the Polar CE Gru|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|volume=335|issue=4|pages=918–22|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?2002MNRAS.335..918R&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf|bibcode=2002MNRAS.335..918R|arxiv=astro-ph/0205102|doi=10.1046/j.1365-8711.2002.05666.x|access-date=2022-04-29|archive-date=2021-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211114160752/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?2002MNRAS.335..918R&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf}}</ref>。

六顆恆星被認為有行星系統。[[天鶴座τ|天鶴座τ<sup>1</sup>]]是一顆6.0等的黃色恆星，位於大約106光年以外<ref>{{cite web |url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=tau1+gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title = Tau1 Gruis -- High proper-motion Star |work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate = 11 February 2014 |archive-date = 2017-12-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171208122553/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=tau1+gru&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url = no }}</ref>。它可能是一顆主序星或是剛開始離開主序的恆星，因為他在膨脹和冷卻中。在2002年，發現這顆恆星可能有一顆行星伴侶<ref name="Jones2003">{{cite journal | title=An Exoplanet in Orbit around τ1 Gruis | url=http://mnras.oxfordjournals.org/content/341/3/948.full | last1=Jones | first1=R. Paul | last2=Butler | first2=Hugh R. A. | last3=Tinney | first3=C. G. | last4=Marcy | first4=Geoffrey W. | last5=Penny | first5=Alan J. | last6=McCarthy | first6=Chris | last7=Carter | first7=Brad D. | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | date=2003 | volume=341 | issue=3 | pages=948–52 | arxiv=astro-ph/0209302 | bibcode=2003MNRAS.341..948J | doi=10.1046/j.1365-8711.2003.06481.x}}</ref>。[[HD_215456|HD 215456]]、[[HD_213240|HD 213240]]和 [[WASP-95|WASP-95]]都是類似太陽的黃色恆星，各有兩顆行星<ref>{{cite arXiv |last1=Mayor |first1=M. |last2=Marmier |first2=M. |last3=Lovis |first3=C. |last4=Udry |first4=S. |last5=Ségransan |first5=D. |last6=Pepe |first6=F. |last7=Benz |first7=W. |last8=Bertaux |first8=J.-L. |last9=Bouchy |first9=F. |last10=Dumusque |first10=X. |last11=Lo Curto |first11=G. |last12=Mordasini |first12=C. |last13=Queloz |first13=D. |last14=Santos |first14=N.C. |display-authors=1
 |date=2011 |title=The HARPS Search for Southern Extra-solar Planets XXXIV. Occurrence, Mass Distribution and Orbital Properties of Super-Earths and Neptune-mass Planets |eprint=1109.2497 |class=astro-ph.EP}}</ref>；一顆遠離[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]的行星<ref name=mugrauer>{{cite journal | url=http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full/2005/36/aa2297-04/aa2297-04.html | last=Mugrauer | first=M. | last2=Neuhäuser | first2=R. | last3=Seifahrt | first3=A. | last4=Mazeh | first4=T. | last5=Guenther | first5=E. | title=Four New Wide Binaries Among Exoplanet Host Stars | journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | date=2005 | volume=440 | issue=3 | pages=1051–60 | doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20042297 | bibcode=2005A&A...440.1051M | arxiv=astro-ph/0507101 | access-date=2017-12-08 | archive-date=2014-02-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225020020/http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full/2005/36/aa2297-04/aa2297-04.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>；還有一顆[[熱木星|熱木星]]WASP-95b，在短短的兩天就繞著這顆母恆星公轉一圈<ref name="hellier13">{{cite journal|author1=Hellier, Coel |author2=Anderson, D.R. |author3=Collier Cameron, A. |author4=Delrez, L. |author5=Gillon, M. |author6=Jehin, E. |author7=Lendl, M. |author8=Maxted, P.F.L. |author9=Pepe, F. |author10=Pollacco, D. |author11=Queloz, D. |author12=Segransan, D. |author13=Smalley, B. |author14=Smith, A.M.S. |author15=Southworth, J. |author16=Triaud, A.H.M.J. |author17=Udry, S. |author18=West, R.G. |date=2014|title=Transiting Hot Jupiters from WASP-South, Euler and TRAPPIST: WASP-95b to WASP-101b|bibcode=2014MNRAS.440.1982H|arxiv=1310.5630|doi=10.1093/mnras/stu410|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society |volume=440 |issue=3 |pages=1982–92}}</ref>。[[葛利斯832|葛利斯832]]是一顆紅矮星，光譜類型M1.5V，視星等8.66，距離16.1光年，是最靠近太陽系的恆星之一。在2008年發現它有一顆類似[[木星|木星]]的行星 －[[格利澤832b|格利澤832b]]，以9.4±0.4年的週期繞行著<ref name="bailey08">{{cite journal |last1=Bailey |first1=J. |last2=Butler |first2=R.P. |last3=Tinney |first3=C.G. |last4=Jones |first4=H.R.A. |last5=O'Toole |first5=S. |last6=Carter |first6=B.D. |last7=Marcy |first7=G. W. |date=2008|title=A Jupiter-like Planet Orbiting the Nearby M Dwarf GJ832 |journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] |volume=690 |issue=1 |pages=743–47 |arxiv=0809.0172 |bibcode=2009ApJ...690..743B |doi=10.1088/0004-637X/690/1/743}}</ref><!-- cites 2 previous sentences -->。[[WISE_2220−3628|WISE 2220−3628]]是一顆光譜型為Y的[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]，有一顆類似恆星的天體很靠近它。經由計算得到與地球的距離是26光年<ref name="Kirkpatrick2012">{{cite journal | authorlink=J. Davy Kirkpatrick | last1=Kirkpatrick | last2=Gelino |first1=J. D. | first2=C. R. | last3=Cushing | first3=M. C. | last4=Mace | first4=G. N. | last5=Griffith | first5=R. L. | last6=Skrutskie | first6=M. F. | last7=Marsh | first7=K. A. | last8=Wright | first8=E. L. | last9=Eisenhardt | first9=P. R. | last10=McLean | first10=I. S. | last11=Mainzer | first11=A. K. | last12=Burgasser | first12=A. J. | last13=Tinney | first13=C. G. | last14=Parker | first14=S. | last15=Salter | first15=G. | title=Further Defining Spectral Type "Y" and Exploring the Low-mass End of the Field Brown Dwarf Mass Function | year=2012 | journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume=753 | issue=2 | page=156 | arxiv=1205.2122 | doi=10.1088/0004-637X/753/2/156 | bibcode=2012ApJ...753..156K}}</ref>。

=== 深空天體 ===
[[File:From_Cosmic_Spare_Tyre_to_Ethereal_Blossom.tif|right]]，備胎星雲是[[ESO|ESO]][[新技術望遠鏡|新技術望遠鏡]]的暗天體光譜儀和照相機（EFOSC2）拍攝的。]]
暱稱為備胎星雲<ref name="ESO12">{{cite web|url=http://www.eso.org/public/images/potw1242a/|title=From Cosmic Spare Tyre to Ethereal Blossom|last=ESO|date=2012|work=Picture of the Week|publisher=European Southern Observatory|accessdate=6 February 2014|archive-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709025511/http://www.eso.org/public/images/potw1242a/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> [[IC_5148|IC 5148]]是[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]]，位置在[[天鶴座λ|天鶴座λ]]西方約1度<ref name="streicher">{{cite web  | last = Streicher  | first = Magda  | date = December 2010  | title = Grus—An Elegant Starry Bird  | publisher = The Astronomical Society of Southern Africa  | work = Deepsky Delights  | url = http://www.mnassa.org.za/html/Dec2010/2010MNASSA..69..Dec..229.pdf  | pages = 56–59  | accessdate = 7 February 2014  | archive-date = 2016-03-04  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103916/http://www.mnassa.org.za/html/Dec2010/2010MNASSA..69..Dec..229.pdf  | dead-url = yes  }}</ref>，距離地球大約3,000光年。它以每秒50公里的速度膨脹，是膨脹速度最快的行星狀星雲之一<ref name="ESO12"/>。

在天鶴座θ的東北方有4個相互作用的星系，稱為天鶴四重奏<ref name=Bakich>{{cite book|last=Bakich|first=Michael E.|title=1,001 Celestial Wonders to See Before You Die|url=https://archive.org/details/celestialwonders00baki_175|date=2010|publisher=Springer Science+Business Media, LLC|location=New York, New York|isbn=978-1-4419-1777-5|page=[https://archive.org/details/celestialwonders00baki_175/page/n346 334]}}</ref>。這些星系是[[NGC_7552|NGC 7552]]、[[NGC_7590|NGC 7590]]、[[NGC_7599|NGC 7599]]、和[[NGC_7582|NGC 7582]]<ref name=koribalski>{{cite web|url=http://www.atnf.csiro.au/people/bkoribal/ngc7582/grus_hi.html|title=The Grus-Quartet|author=Koribalski, Bärbel|date=1996|accessdate=28 January 2014|archive-date=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031212511/http://www.atnf.csiro.au/people/bkoribal/ngc7582/grus_hi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後面三個星系在天空中只佔據了10角分的跨度，有時被稱為"天鶴三重奏"，然而所有4個星系是一個更大更鬆散的星系團，被稱為天鶴群IC 1459的一部分<ref name="O'Meara"/>。NGC 7552和7582是高度活躍的[[星暴星系|星暴星系]]，而這被認為是潮汐力相互作用產生的<ref name=koribalski/>。位於天鶴座與南魚座邊界的<ref name="streicher"/>[[IC_1459|IC 1459]]是一個特殊的E3巨大[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]]，它有一個快速[[反向旋轉螺旋槳|反向旋轉]]的恆星核，外面的區域有波紋的外殼層<ref>{{cite journal |author= Verdoes Kleijn, Gijs A.; van der Marel, Roeland P.;  [[C._Marcella_Carollo|Carollo, C. Marcella]]; de Zeeuw, P. Tim |date=2000|title=The Black Hole in IC 1459 from Hubble Space Telescope Observations of the Ionized Gas Disk|journal=The Astronomical Journal|volume=120|pages=1221–37 |url=http://iopscience.iop.org/1538-3881/120/3/1221/fulltext/|arxiv = astro-ph/0003433 |bibcode = 2000AJ....120.1221V |doi = 10.1086/301524 }}</ref><!-- cites previous two sentences -->。這個星系的視星等為11.9等<ref>{{cite web |url =http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=IC+1459+&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |title =IC 1459 – LINER-type Active Galaxy Nucleus |work =SIMBAD Astronomical Database |publisher =Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg |accessdate =7 February 2014 |archive-date =2017-12-10 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171210123911/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=IC+1459+&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |dead-url =no }}</ref>，距離大約在8,000萬光年<ref name="streicher"/>。

[[NGC_7424|NGC 7424]]是視星等10.4等的[[棒渦星系|棒渦星系]]<ref>{{cite web|url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC+7424|title = NGC 7424 – Galaxy in Group of Galaxies|work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database|publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg|accessdate = 4 February 2014|archive-date = 2016-04-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160415190631/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC%207424|dead-url = no}}</ref>，位置在天鶴三重奏西方約4度<ref name="streicher"/>，距離大約3,750萬光年，直徑約10萬光年，有完好的螺旋臂，被認為與銀河系相像<ref>{{Cite APOD|title=Grand Spiral Galaxy NGC 7424 |date=8 January 2013|access-date=4 February 2014}}</ref>。在NGC 7424 觀測到2個{{link-en|超亮X射線源|ultraluminous X-ray source}}和一顆[[超新星|超新星]]<ref name="soria06">{{cite journal |author1=Soria, R. |author2=Kuncic, Z. |author3=Broderick, J. W. |author4=Ryder, S. D. | title = Multiband Study of NGC 7424 and its Two Newly-discovered ULXs | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society |date=2006 | volume = 370 | issue = 4 | pages = 1666–76 | bibcode = 2006MNRAS.370.1666S | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2006.10629.x|arxiv = astro-ph/0606080 }}</ref>。[[SN_2001ig|SN 2001ig]] 是在2001年發現的，類型是[[超新星#II型超新星|IIb超新星]]，在它的光譜中最初顯示微弱的氫線，但是後來又檢測不到，並且被氧、鎂和鈣的譜線取代；而且其它的特徵類似[[超新星#I型超新星|Ib超新星]]<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Maund, Justyn R. |author2=Wheeler, J. Craig |author3=Patat, Ferdinando |author4=Wang, Lifan |author5=Baade, Dietrich |author6=Höflich, Peter A. |date=2007|title=Spectropolarimetry of the Type IIb Supernova 2001ig*|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=671|issue=2|pages=1944–1958|arxiv = 0709.1487 |bibcode = 2007ApJ...671.1944M |doi = 10.1086/523261 }}</ref>。一顆[[光譜類型|光譜類型]]為F、A或B的大質量恆星被認為是存活下來的SN 2001jg伴星，可能是顆[[沃夫–瑞葉星|沃夫–瑞葉星]]<ref name="ryder06">{{cite journal |author1=Ryder, Stuart D. |author2=Murrowood, Clair E. |author3=Stathakis, Raylee A. | title = A Post-mortem Investigation of the Type IIb Supernova 2001ig| journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | date = 2006 | volume = 369
| issue = 1 | pages = L32–L36 | bibcode = 2006MNRAS.369L..32R| doi = 10.1111/j.1745-3933.2006.00168.x|arxiv = astro-ph/0603336 }}</ref>。

鄰近鶴一的[[NGC_7213|NGC 7213]]<ref name="streicher"/>是正面朝向[[地球|地球]]的I型[[西佛星系|西佛星系]]，距離大約7,170萬光年<ref name="hameed">{{cite journal|author1=Hameed, Salman|author2=Blank, David L.|author3=Young, Lisa M.|author4=Devereux, Nick|date=2001|title=The Discovery of a Giant Hα Filament in NGC 7213|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=546|issue=2|pages=L97–L100|url=http://cds.cern.ch/record/476765/files/0011208.pdf|arxiv=astro-ph/0011208|bibcode=2001ApJ...546L..97H|doi=10.1086/318865|access-date=2017-12-10|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224231211/http://cds.cern.ch/record/476765/files/0011208.pdf}}</ref>。它的視星等為12.1等<ref>{{cite web|url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC%207213|title = NGC 7213 – Type 1 Seyfert Galaxy|work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database|publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg|accessdate = 5 February 2014|archive-date = 2017-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171210123922/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC%207213|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在可見光的觀測是寧靜的，但在較長波長的觀察顯示發生碰撞或合併的跡象，而電離氫的擾動模式包括長6萬4千光年的氣體絲<ref name="hameed"/>。它是由10個星系組成的星系群成員之一<ref name=fouque>{{cite journal|last=Fouque, P.; Proust, D.; Quintana, H.; Ramirez, A.|title=Dynamics of the Pavo-Indus and Grus Clouds of Galaxies|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics Supplement Series|volume=100|issue=3|pages=493–500|bibcode=1993A&AS..100..493F|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1993A%26AS..100..493F&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf|last2=Proust|first2=D.|last3=Quintana|first3=H.|last4=Ramirez|first4=A.|year=1993|access-date=2020-10-06|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404173915/http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1993A%26AS..100..493F&data_type=PDF_HIGH&whole_paper=YES&type=PRINTER&filetype=.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[NGC_7410|NGC 7410]]是英國天文學家[[約翰·赫歇爾|約翰·赫歇爾]]在[[好望角|好望角]]觀測時，於1843年10月發現的一個[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]。這個星系的視星等是11.7等，距離地球大約1億2,200萬光年<ref name="O'Meara">{{cite book|last=O'Meara|first=Stephen James|title=Deep Sky Companions: Southern Gems|date=2013|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=New York, New York|isbn=978-1-107-01501-2|pages=418–26|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC%207213|access-date=2017-12-10|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210123922/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=NGC%207213|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

